---
title: "Projects"
layout: "layouts/page.njk"
description: "Open-source tools, homelab infrastructure, and side projects."
image: "/assets/images/jesus.webp"
---

<div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
{%- for project in projects -%}
  <div class="panel panel-rack">
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
      <i class="fa-solid {{ project.icon }}" style="color: var(--accent); font-size: 1.2rem;"></i>
      <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.25rem;">{{ project.name }}</h3>
    </div>
    <p class="muted" style="font-size: 0.875rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; line-height: 1.55;">{{ project.description | safe }}</p>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.35rem;">
      {%- if project.link -%}
        <a href="{{ project.link }}" class="tag tag-accent" target="_blank" rel="noopener">source</a>
      {%- endif -%}
      {%- for tag in project.tags -%}
        <span class="tag">{{ tag }}</span>
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>
  </div>
{%- endfor -%}
</div>

<h2 class="section-heading">// Infrastructure</h2>

<p class="muted" style="max-width: 600px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
All services run on a Proxmox-based homelab behind <strong>OPNsense</strong> with nginx-proxy-manager for reverse proxy and SSL termination, and oauth2-proxy for authentication.
</p>

